Here is my 4th module assignment on JavaScript Calculator.

The whole project is done using the bootstarp and javascript. 

1. There is and hovering effect on the submit button, 
   including transform property and text-style.

2. Also the active effect where the text turns to italic style.

3. The borders are provided with different colors and border size.

4. Onchange and Oninput events have been applied to clear the answer field,
   when there is change in the input fields of number and the operator.